.ipynb_checkpoints/

# OS files
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store

# Excel lock files
~$*

# ── Autoresearch artifact overrides ──────────────────────────────────────────
# The blanket *.csv / *.pdf / *.png rules above are there to keep clinical data
# and large figures out of git. These overrides re-allow the aggregate result
# files generated by runs/, figures/, and paper/ — none of which contain PHI.
!runs/**/*.csv
!runs/**/*.json
!runs/**/*.pdf
!runs/**/*.png
!experiments.jsonl
!dashboard.md
!research_log.md
!figures/**/*.pdf
!figures/**/*.png
!figures/**/*.svg
!paper/**/*.pdf
!paper/**/*.png
